source:
TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Aarner is staring mournfully over the railing.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête
Aarner a perdu des lettres très importantes.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_TODO_00<tab>Collect tearstained letters in the Derelicts.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_TODO_00<tab>Aller ramasser les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8EA70302 /var> à La Fange

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the tearstained letters to Aarner near the Grand Dame's Parlor.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_TODO_01<tab>Ramener les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8EA70302 /var> à Aarner, près du salon de la Grande Dame

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_000<tab>My letters! Scattered by the winds! Whose idea was it to build this city with so many breezy walkways?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_000<tab>J'ai fait tomber mes lettres et le vent les a emportées jusqu'à La Fange<var 1D /var>! Il est crucial que je les récupère<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_001<tab><sigh> No. In this, too, I have no one to blame but myself. They are important to me, though, so might I ask you to search for them? There are three, all told. They likely came to rest in the Derelicts, as these things tend to.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_001<tab>J'irais bien les chercher moi-même, mais je ne peux pas laisser mon échoppe vide<var 1D /var>! Si jamais tu vas vers La Fange, pourrais-tu les ramasser et me les ramener<var 1D /var>? Il y en a trois<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_002<tab>I would fetch the letters myself, but I'm meant to be meeting someone here, and I don't believe I could stand to disappoint yet another person.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_002<tab>J'irais bien les chercher moi-même, mais je ne peux pas laisser mon échoppe vide<var 1D /var>! Si jamais tu vas vers La Fange, pourrais-tu me ramasser et me ramener mes trois lettres<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_010<tab>Ah, there you are. Did you have any luck?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_010<tab>Oh<var 1D /var>! Je t'attendais<var 1D /var>! Tu as pu retrouver mes lettres<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_011<tab>You found all three! Wonderful! I cannot possibly express how difficult it would have been for me to rewrite them.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_011<tab>Oui, c'est bien elles<var 1D /var>! Ahhhh, je suis tellement soulagé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_012<tab>Wait... Now I've had a good look at you─are you perchance one of those responsible for freeing us from Vauthry's influence?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_012<tab>Mais... Attends<var 1D /var>! Maintenant que je te regarde de plus près, je te reconnais<var 1D /var>! C'est bien toi qui étais au centre des récents évènements d'Eulmore, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_013<tab>I thought as much. You have my thanks, for opening my eyes.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_013<tab>J'en étais sûr<var 1D /var>! Grâce à toi et tes compagnons, j'ai enfin ouvert les yeux<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_014<tab>I used to reside in the Crystarium, you know. But the moment that I saw for myself what happens when the eaters take a person... I truly understood, for the first time, that our world teeters on the brink of destruction. I was terrified.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_014<tab>Il y a très longtemps, j'habitais à Cristarium... Jusqu'à ce que je sois témoin d'une attaque de purgateurs. J'ai cru la fin du monde arrivée...

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_015<tab>I knew I could do nothing to change fate. So I came to Eulmore, hoping to forget it instead. Abandoned my work, my family...everything. And I felt no guilt for it, convinced as I was that nothing mattered.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_015<tab>J'ai donc quitté famille et collègues pour m'enfuir à Eulmore, qui promettait de protéger ses habitants....

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_016<tab>Now, though, the scales have fallen from my eyes. I've always been a coward, and what I did was a betrayal of the highest order. And I know...I know there's no going back.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_016<tab>Et aujourd'hui j'ai l'impression de me réveiller comme après un long coma, et je regrette tellement mes actes... Je... Je ne suis qu'un moins-que-rien<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_017<tab>If nothing else, however, I can apologize for what I've done. So I labored over these letters, hoping to convey my contrition. I don't expect forgiveness, but I hope it might mean something, at least, to those I left behind.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_017<tab>Je n'ai pas le courage d'aller voir ma famille et mes collègues, mais je leur ai écrit de longues lettres d'excuses, celles que tu es allé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> me chercher.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_018<tab>I cannot alter what has been done, but I can change myself. Try to be better. And you will always have my gratitude for giving me the ability to see that─you and your elven friend, both. Thank you.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH009_03519_AARNER_000_018<tab>Vraiment, merci beaucoup<var 1D /var>! Remercie tes compagnons elfes qui se sont battus contre Vauthry aussi, quand tu les verras<var 1D /var>!
